No. 10A357. Family PAC, Applicant v. Rob McKenna, Attorney General of Washington, et al. 562 U.S. 958, 131 S. Ct. 500,

178 L. Ed. 2d 284,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8126. October 12, 2010.

Application to vacate the stay entered by the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit, case No. 10-35832, addressed to Justice Kennedy and by him referred to the Court, denied.
